cql_libraries.cql:
library MeasureUsingNewQDMElementsandAttributes version '0.0.002'

using QDM version '5.5'

codesystem "LOINC": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.6.1'
codesystem "UMLS": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.6.86'
codesystem "NCI": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.26.1.1'
codesystem "ActPriority": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.7'
codesystem "ActCode": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.4'
codesystem "HSLOC": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.6.259'
codesystem "SNOMEDCT": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.6.96'
codesystem "ICD10CM": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.6.90'
codesystem "SNOMEDCT:2019-03": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.6.96' version 'urn:hl7:version:2019-03'

valueset "Acute Inpatient": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.101.12.1083'
valueset "Consultant Report": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.121.12.1006'
valueset "Essential Hypertension": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.104.12.1011'
valueset "Ethnicity": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.114222.4.11.837'
valueset "ONC Administrative Sex": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113762.1.4.1'
valueset "Payer": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.114222.4.11.3591'
valueset "Race": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.114222.4.11.836'
valueset "Referral": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.101.12.1046'

code "Cholesterol [Mass/volume] in Serum or Plasma": '2093-3' from "LOINC" display 'Cholesterol [Mass/volume] in Serum or Plasma'
code "Condition present on admission": 'C4554448' from "UMLS" display 'Condition present on admission'
code "Doctor of Medicine": 'C39383' from "NCI" display 'Doctor of Medicine'
code "Doctor of Osteopathic Medicine": 'C39385' from "NCI" display 'Doctor of Osteopathic Medicine'
code "elective": 'EL' from "ActPriority" display 'elective'
code "General": 'GENRL' from "ActCode" display 'General'
code "Inpatient Medical Ward": '1060-3' from "HSLOC" display 'Inpatient Medical Ward'
code "Lipid 1996 panel - Serum or Plasma": '24331-1' from "LOINC" display 'Lipid 1996 panel - Serum or Plasma'
code "Medical doctor (occupation)": '112247003' from "SNOMEDCT" display 'Medical doctor (occupation)'
code "Morbid (severe) obesity due to excess calories": 'E66.01' from "ICD10CM" display 'Morbid (severe) obesity due to excess calories'
code "Oncology": 'ONC' from "ActCode" display 'Oncology'
code "Weight loss (amount) (observable entity)": '363806002' from "SNOMEDCT:2019-03" display 'Weight loss (amount) (observable entity)'

parameter "Measurement Period" Interval<DateTime>

context Patient

/*Supplemental Data Element Definitions*/

define "SDE Ethnicity":
  ["Patient Characteristic Ethnicity": "Ethnicity"]

define "SDE Payer":
  ["Patient Characteristic Payer": "Payer"]

define "SDE Race":
  ["Patient Characteristic Race": "Race"]

define "SDE Sex":
  ["Patient Characteristic Sex": "ONC Administrative Sex"]

/*Population level definitions*/

define "Initial Population":
  "Has Qualifying Inpatient Encounter"
    and "Has Appropriate Labs Run"
    and "Has Consultant Report From Referring Provider"

define "Denominator":
  "Initial Population"

define "Numerator":
  "Has Care Goal Set"

/*CQL logic using entity types: Practitioner, PatientEntity, CarePartner, Organization (using identifier attribute)*/

define "Inpatient Encounters with Appropriate Entity Identifiers":
  ["Encounter, Performed": "Acute Inpatient"] Inpt
    where ( Inpt.participant is PatientEntity
        and Inpt.participant.identifier.namingSystem = 'Medical Record Number'
        and Inpt.participant.identifier.value = '1321324544'
    )
      or ( Inpt.participant is Practitioner
          and Inpt.participant.identifier.namingSystem = 'NPI'
          and Inpt.participant.identifier.value = '1321324522'
      )
      or ( Inpt.participant is Organization
          and Inpt.participant.identifier.namingSystem = 'TIN'
          and Inpt.participant.identifier.value = '224567893'
      )
      or ( Inpt.participant is CarePartner
          and Inpt.participant.identifier.namingSystem = 'System Id'
          and Inpt.participant.identifier.value = '123023134'
      )

/*CQL logic using "Care Goal" QDM type.*/

define "Has Care Goal Set":
  exists ( ["Care Goal": "Weight loss (amount) (observable entity)"] WeightGoal
      where WeightGoal.statusDate during "Measurement Period"
        and WeightGoal.relevantPeriod during "Measurement Period"
        and exists ( ["Diagnosis": "Essential Hypertension"] Hypertension
            where Hypertension.id in WeightGoal.relatedTo
        )
        and ( WeightGoal.targetOutcome = 5
            or WeightGoal.targetOutcome = 5.0
            or WeightGoal.targetOutcome = 5 '[lb_av]'
        )
        and ( WeightGoal.performer is PatientEntity
            and WeightGoal.performer.identifier.namingSystem = 'Medical Record Number'
            and WeightGoal.performer.identifier.value = 'MR-2124A2424'
        )
  )

define "First Referral During Measurement Period":
  First(["Intervention, Performed": "Referral"] ReferralPerformed
      where ReferralPerformed.relevantPeriod starts during "Measurement Period"
      sort by authorDatetime
  )

define "Has Consultant Report From Referring Provider":
  exists ( ["Communication, Performed": "Consultant Report"] ConsultantReportCommunicated
      with "First Referral During Measurement Period" FirstReferralPerformed
        such that FirstReferralPerformed.id in ConsultantReportCommunicated.relatedTo
          and ConsultantReportCommunicated.authorDatetime after start of FirstReferralPerformed.relevantPeriod
                //sender criteria
      where ( ConsultantReportCommunicated.sender is Practitioner
          and ConsultantReportCommunicated.sender.role ~ "Medical doctor (occupation)"
          and ConsultantReportCommunicated.sender.specialty ~ "Oncology"
          and ConsultantReportCommunicated.sender.qualification ~ "Doctor of Osteopathic Medicine"
          and ConsultantReportCommunicated.sender.identifier.namingSystem = 'National Provider Identifier'
          and ConsultantReportCommunicated.sender.identifier.value = '1321354654'
      )
            //recipient criteria
        and ( ConsultantReportCommunicated.recipient is Practitioner
            and ConsultantReportCommunicated.recipient.role ~ "Medical doctor (occupation)"
            and ConsultantReportCommunicated.recipient.specialty ~ "General"
            and ConsultantReportCommunicated.recipient.qualification ~ "Doctor of Medicine"
            and ConsultantReportCommunicated.recipient.identifier.namingSystem = 'National Provider Identifier'
            and ConsultantReportCommunicated.recipient.identifier.value = '3324546165'
        )
  )

define "Has Qualifying Inpatient Encounter":
  exists ( "Inpatient Encounters with Appropriate Entity Identifiers" Inpt
      where Inpt.priority ~ "elective"
        and exists ( Inpt.diagnoses Dx
            where Dx.code ~ "Morbid (severe) obesity due to excess calories"
              and Dx.rank = 1
              and Dx.presentOnAdmissionIndicator ~ "Condition present on admission"
        )
        and exists ( Inpt.facilityLocations fc
            where fc.code ~ "Inpatient Medical Ward"
              and fc.locationPeriod ends during "Measurement Period"
        )
        and Inpt.priority is not null
        and exists ( ["Procedure, Performed"] Px
            where Px.relevantDatetime during Inpt.relevantPeriod
              and Px.rank = 1
              and Px.priority ~ "elective"
        )
  )

define "Has Appropriate Labs Run":
  exists ( ["Laboratory Test, Performed": "Lipid 1996 panel - Serum or Plasma"] CholesterolPanel
      where exists ( CholesterolPanel.components totCholComponent
          where totCholComponent.code ~ "Cholesterol [Mass/volume] in Serum or Plasma"
            and totCholComponent.result > 220 'mg/dL'
      )
        and ( CholesterolPanel.relevantDatetime during "Measurement Period"
            or start of CholesterolPanel.relevantPeriod during "Measurement Period"
        )
        and CholesterolPanel.resultDatetime during "Measurement Period"
  )
